159
00:09:39,851 --> 00:09:42,108
Tama? Ayos lang ba?

160
00:09:42,448 --> 00:09:43,996
Susunduin kita agad kapag tapos na ako.

161
00:09:44,521 --> 00:09:45,259
Okay?

162
00:09:46,432 --> 00:09:48,608
Ayan, ayan.

163
00:09:49,376 --> 00:09:50,688
Heto na.

164
00:09:52,832 --> 00:09:53,536
Naku!

165
00:10:03,528 --> 00:10:05,600
Nanay? Nanay?

166
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:06,368
Oo?

167
00:10:07,424 --> 00:10:08,000
Ah.

168
00:10:08,951 --> 00:10:10,044
Ano 'yon, sinta?

169
00:10:10,740 --> 00:10:12,755
Pakiusap, alagaan mo si Singto para sa akin.

170
00:10:13,408 --> 00:10:14,175
Halika rito, sinta.

171
00:10:15,552 --> 00:10:16,640
Mm, halika rito.

172
00:10:16,844 --> 00:10:19,541
Mahal, huwag mong kalimutan
ang pag-aalaga ng bata noong nakaraang buwan.

173
00:10:20,847 --> 00:10:24,509
Sige. Aasikasuhin ko 'yan
sa susunod na isa o dalawang araw.

174
00:10:24,509 --> 00:10:25,630
(Pangangalaga sa bata, Anne)

175
00:10:25,630 --> 00:10:27,093
- Pasensya na.
- Ayos lang.

176
00:10:27,648 --> 00:10:28,186
Tama.

177
00:10:28,186 --> 00:10:32,572
Wayu, sa tingin ko talaga dapat mong dalhin
si Singto sa doktor.

178
00:10:32,955 --> 00:10:36,149
Hindi siya nagsasalita, at halos wala siyang
reaksyon sa kahit ano.

179
00:10:38,633 --> 00:10:40,064
Sige. Maraming salamat.

180
00:10:40,096 --> 00:10:40,608
Sige.

181
00:10:40,834 --> 00:10:42,892
Pakiusap, alagaan mo siya. Paalam.

182
00:10:42,892 --> 00:10:43,871
Tara na.

183
00:10:59,373 --> 00:11:01,970
(Pwede ba tayong magkita ngayon?)

184
00:11:01,970 --> 00:11:04,767
(Paano kung alas-5 ng hapon?)

185
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:12,219
(Maganda pakinggan. May
gusto akong pag-usapan.)

186
00:11:12,219 --> 00:11:14,717
(Magkita tayo ng 5 PM.)

187
