190
00:11:55,402 --> 00:12:01,733
♪Sana makakita ako nang malinaw,
kahit kaunti pa♪

191
00:12:01,733 --> 00:12:07,908
♪Para hindi ko na kailangang patuloy
na umasa nang palihim nang ganito♪

192
00:12:07,908 --> 00:12:14,154
♪Hindi mo ba lilinawin?
Napakabuti mo sa akin♪

193
00:12:14,154 --> 00:12:19,690
♪Ikaw ba ang hindi malinaw,
o sadyang mali lang ang nakikita ko?♪

194
00:12:21,152 --> 00:12:24,000
♪Higit pa rito, higit pa rito♪

195
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:27,264
♪Higit pa rito, higit pa rito♪

196
00:12:27,264 --> 00:12:32,128
♪Higit pa rito♪

197
00:12:43,339 --> 00:12:44,106
Wayu.

198
00:12:55,456 --> 00:12:56,608
Aray!

199
00:12:57,308 --> 00:12:58,117
Digmaan.

200
00:12:58,557 --> 00:13:01,282
Nagkikita tayo sa ganitong liblib na lugar,
akala ko papatayin mo na ako.

201
00:13:03,937 --> 00:13:06,719
Ganyan talaga ang buhay detektib.
Masasanay ka rin diyan.

202
00:13:08,110 --> 00:13:08,934
